COMPONENTS:

This directory should contain ONLY generic / core COMPONENTS

Examples: navigation bar, tool bar, status bar, etc. 

Components on Pages:

1) if component is used ONLY on one page, place component in '/ pages / [page_name] / [component_name].js'
2) if component is used on MULTIPLE pages, place component in '/ components / [component_name] / [component_name].js'